{"tid":633370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】澳洲查中國鐵路輪轂傾鎖","createTime":"2018-04-18T09:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T13:55:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a51f93f05dcc60d2a35af1bbab5ce3f580df79","tid":633370,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"【貿易戰】澳洲查中國鐵路輪轂傾鎖<br />\n<br />\n中美由貿易戰打到科技戰，最新澳洲亦不甘寂寞，澳洲反傾銷委員會正式對中國鐵路輪轂（Railway Wheels）作反傾銷反補貼調查。據悉中國2017年對澳出口該鐵路輪轂額達770萬美元。此外原產地為法國的進口鐵路輪轂亦被立案作反傾銷調查。<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180418&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58088399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180418%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58088399&d=tqRGKOaiWHhoCo5CzJ7%2BzgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a681370d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180418%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58088399&h=3bf6df68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180418&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58088399</a>"},{"pid":"a03747a7ce4dc9cbcb82ab78d8cec2d0e5bb678a","tid":633370,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:12:30.000Z","msg":"390 1186?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6495ea41d2071135749b0b4bc2ce17d756e40e8a","tid":633370,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e176d5baa49c7e5f9e056dced48cd60d458f5d7","tid":633370,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T11:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19851c3c0afb0fa87ffb515ca6c105afd0d81dfb","tid":633370,"uid":104699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T13:45:53.000Z","msg":"圍住黎屌，華春蠅一次含唔含得晒"},{"pid":"73aaa16b7338802